{"tid":392074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想讚下香港警察","createTime":"2017-09-08T09:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T09:53:49.000Z","uid":139934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2f2d18c6f522beb80dbcd81e25a889b64b0141","tid":392074,"uid":139934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺尖沙咀金馬倫道 <br />\n見到有個師奶好大聲喺到鬧一班外國遊客<br />\n話佢地又惡又唔知乜柒<br />\n但係我經過嘅時候又見唔到班外國人出聲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時有兩個警察喺到調停緊<br />\n雖然我係咁啱經過<br />\n唔知成件事嘅來龍去脈係點<br />\n但係呢件事都唔係重點<br />\n重點係當我經過兩個警察同個師奶後面嘅時候<br />\n聽到其中一個警察細細聲喺個師奶耳邊講...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「啲鬼佬係咁架喇」</span><br />\n<br />\n我當堂嚇一跳 然後得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為黑警淨係識濫用暴力<br />\n原來已經超越左<br />\n仲識得用呢個方式去平息紛爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade7dff89ace499e8f4d50131bca6ace8bfa65cd","tid":392074,"uid":9328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"然後同鬼佬講，d c9 is it la, dont care man!"},{"pid":"94b61db02047f481b8e72ba455a8f0aeffc7e490","tid":392074,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:09:15.000Z","msg":"警犬本身就一個笑話 乜都得過且過 唔使寫reort就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451c87ef88de84957ad97bc38d61b576f4616f47","tid":392074,"uid":4723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"梗係啦<br />\n一陣要同鬼佬落口供咪仆街"}]}